OL,3,CFears remain for town's future three
OL,4,Cmonths after floods
OL,6,FThree months on from the devastating
OL,7,Ffloods, Downpatrick's major
OL,8,Fsupermarket has reopened, but fears
OL,9,Fremain for the town's future.
OL,11,FASDA opened a new store on Thursday,
OL,12,Fbringing hope that trade is getting
OL,13,Fback on track.
OL,15,FHowever, many businesses remain shut,
OL,16,Fhaving suffered thousands of pounds
OL,17,Fworth of damage when the flooding hit
OL,18,Flast October.
