OL,4,Cmonths after floods
OL,6,FOf the #15million promised by the
OL,7,Fgovernment, just over #1m has been
OL,8,Fpaid out. That's 143 grants of #7,500
OL,9,Fto aid essential repairs.
OL,11,FTraders in the Co Down town have told
OL,12,FUTV the money barely begins to cover
OL,13,Fthe costs.
OL,15,F"Whole equipment everything is gone,"
OL,16,Fsaid Orhan Guzel, whose takeaway
OL,17,Fsuffered #100,000 worth of damage and
OL,18,Fhasn't been able to reopen.
OL,20,F"The flooding was up to my chest."
