OL,6,FInformation on how to apply for a
OL,7,Fsecond bout of funding, was expected
OL,8,Fto be announced in early January.
OL,10,FIt's nearly February and those details
OL,11,Fare still being finalised.
OL,13,FThe Department for the Economy says a
OL,14,Fbusiness case is still being developed
OL,15,Fand will only open when approved by
OL,16,Fthe Treasury.
