OL,6,F"The Department is working closely
OL,7,Fwith the district Council on the
OL,8,Fdetails of the follow up scheme to
OL,9,Fassist the most severely affected
OL,10,Fsmall and medium sized businesses," a
OL,11,Fstatement said.
OL,13,F"We have also been looking at how we
OL,14,Fdesign the details of the support
OL,15,Fscheme to address some of the issues
OL,16,Fthat have been raised with us by
OL,17,Fbusinesses and local representatives
OL,18,Fto make sure that it will effectively
OL,19,Fdeal with the realities on the ground.
